nb_of_inputs - Variable in class NeuralNetwork.Neuron.Neuron

nbOfColors - Variable in class NeuralNetwork.NeuralNetwork
Describes how many colors are to be classified (nb of output neurons)
nbOfNeurons - Variable in class NeuralNetwork.Layers.Layer
Describes the number of neurons in the Layer.
NeuralNetwork - package NeuralNetwork
Regroups all components that are directly part of the neural network
NeuralNetwork - Class in NeuralNetwork
Represents a neural network containing one input layer with 3 inputs, two hidden layer with a variable number of neurons and one output layer containing a variable amount of output neurons (depending on how many colors are to be detected).
NeuralNetwork(int, int) - Constructor for class NeuralNetwork.NeuralNetwork
Create a neural network with the following topology: Input Layer: 3 input nodes (R/G/B) + bias 2 hidden Layer with a variable amount of neurons (-n flag) Output Layer: variable amount of neurons (-c flag)
Model.NeuralNetwork.Layers - package NeuralNetwork.Layers
Regroups the different layer types used in the neural network.
Model.NeuralNetwork.Neuron - package NeuralNetwork.Neuron
Regroups different Neuron types used in the Neural network
Neuron - Class in Model.NeuralNetwork.Neuron

Neuron(int) - Constructor for class NeuralNetwork.Neuron.Neuron

neuronOutput - Variable in class NeuralNetwork.Neuron.Neuron

neurons - Variable in class NeuralNetwork.Layers.Layer
